el 550 (MTV China)\n<small>([[Indonesia]])</small>\n| iptv serv 3 = [[Oxygen TV]] \n| iptv serv 4 = [[Unifi TV]] <small>([[Malaysia]])</small>\n| iptv chan 4 = Channel 241 (MTV China)\n(Coming Soon)\n}}\n'''MTV Mandarin''' is a 24-hour music channel which airs Chinese and international music programs owned by [[ViacomCBS Networks EMEAA]]. One of the first three MTV Asia channels along with [[MTV Asia]] and [[MTV India]]. MTV Mandarin has two different feeds. The channel broadcasts in China, Taiwan, Hong Kong, Singapore, Malaysia and Indonesia.\n\n==Operating channels==\n* MTV Hong Kong - based in [[Hong Kong]]\n* MTV Taiwan - based in [[Taipei]]\n* MTV China - based in [[Beijing]] and [[Shanghai]]\n\n==Shows==\n{{Main|List of programmes broadcast by MTV in Asia}}\n\n==Current VJs==\n* George Chang\n* Andy Chen\n* Emma\n* Stacy Hsu\n* Sammy Hu\n* Katherine\n* [[Linda Liao]]\n* Meimei\n* Tony\n\n==See also==\n* [[MTV (Music Television)]]\n* [[MTV Networks Asia Pacific]]\n* [[MTV Southeast Asia]]\n\n==External links==\n* [http://www.mtvchina.com/ MTV China] {{in lang|zh}}\n* [http://www.mtv.com.tw/ MTV Taiwan] {{in lang|zh}}\n\n{{MTV Networks}}\n\n{{Television in Hong Kong}}\n{{Television in the Republic of China}}\n{{Television in the People's Republic of China}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Mtv Mandarin}}\n[[Category:Television stations in Taiwan]]\n[[Category:Television channels and stations established in 1995]]\n[[Category:Television stations in Hong Kong]]\n[[Category:Television in China]]\n[[Category:Chinese television networks]]\n[[Category:MTV channels]]\n[[Category:Companies based in Taipei]]\n[[Category:Music organizations based in China]]\n{{Taiwan-tv-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox TV channel |\n| name = MTV Mandarin\n| logofile          = MTV Logo 2010.png\n| logosize          = 150px\n| country = Hong Kong <br> Taiwan <br> China\n| broadcast area = Hong Kong, Taiwan, Mainland China and Chinese communities across Asia\n| headquarters = [[Singapore]]<br />[[Taiwan]]